items.title: My #wcw is @nathallie__ I have to say when you came and sat your shot little self next to me on your first day of show choir I never expected we would be where we are now, 110 miles apart and still best friends. I picked three pics from when we first became best friends until now. We are pretty much opposites but yet there is no one I would rather spend a day with than you. We have more memories and inside jokes than I can court because every time we see each other we make new ones. I can't wait till you can drive up here and visit me like every weekend. I'm so proud of you for everything you've done this year! I know that you will be there for me no matter what, and that means even more to me right now than usual. I hope you're rocking it out at Showcase tonight! If you could tell by the rest of this post I love you and miss you and can't wait to see you in 9 days! (: #bestfriend #loveher #missher #somuch #puertorican
